&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-src=&#34;https://free-img.400040.xyz/4/2025/04/26/680bc1708eecf.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20250426010759948&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
